---
import StoryBand from "./StoryBand.astro";
import mariaWithNala from "../images/maria-with-nala.webp";
---

<StoryBand
    image={mariaWithNala}
    imageAlt="A member of the Davis family hugging Nala as a puppy"
    eyebrow="The good part"
    title="One very good girl"
    reverse
>
    <p>
        Before Nala, the Davis family had never had a dog. We learned as we went
        — the walks, the chewed shoes, the 3&nbsp;a.m. wake-up calls — and
        somewhere in there she became the heart of the house.
    </p>
    <p>
        She's happiest with her people, a good nap spot, and the faint
        possibility of a treat.
    </p>
</StoryBand>
